{"tid":1399368,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曼聯8500萬鎊不含浮動條款簽麥佳亞","createTime":"2019-08-03T06:56:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T09:47:41.000Z","uid":173952,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"96bc7d4c29be4f736bf4b37a79bd3e9896843f90","tid":1399368,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T06:56:20.000Z","msg":"據英國媒體報導，曼聯與李斯特城就麥佳亞的轉會費達成協議，金額為8500萬英鎊。<br />\n  《太陽報》披露，這8500萬英鎊，將由曼聯全額支付現金，不包含任何浮動條款（will be paid in cash without add-ons）。<br />\n  兩年前，李斯特城從候城簽下麥佳亞時，花費是1700萬英鎊，兩年後轉手再賣，可謂賺頭豐厚。8500萬英鎊這個金額，打破了利物浦簽入雲迪積克時的後衛身價紀錄（7500萬英鎊），而且足足多出了1000萬。<br />\n  另外在英超球會收購榜上，麥佳亞的8500萬英鎊排在第二位，第一是曼聯當年以8900萬英鎊簽下普巴。<br />\n  據多家英國媒體報導，接下來麥佳亞將參加曼聯的體檢，通過之後，26歲的他將與紅魔簽下一份為期六年的長約。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5efacaf86f05c8bf76a94173b4367000ab3ec649","tid":1399368,"uid":67225,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:02:09.000Z","msg":"8000定8500呀<br />\n媽呀我好亂呀"},{"pid":"df6f8e793981173b39bb3a462042700a5a756a57","tid":1399368,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:05:54.000Z","msg":"40萬磅周薪？"},{"pid":"d6f239c9413dfa1891b81f6c37a335694d2e2892","tid":1399368,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df6f8e793981173b39bb3a462042700a5a756a57","tid":1399368,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:05:54.000Z","msg":"40萬磅周薪？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:11:04.000Z","msg":"60"},{"pid":"e931648faf79ad979800e836c4e987c447c8c278","tid":1399368,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d6f239c9413dfa1891b81f6c37a335694d2e2892","tid":1399368,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df6f8e793981173b39bb3a462042700a5a756a57","tid":1399368,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:05:54.000Z","msg":"40萬磅周薪？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:11:04.000Z","msg":"60"},"citedBy":0,"re